Title: An Act Changing the Name of the Manuk Mangkaw East Elementary School in the Municipality of Simunul, Province of Tawi-Tawi, to Hadji Imam Banjal Elementary School
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 567
An Act Changing the Name of the Manuk Mangkaw East Elementary School in the Municipality of Simunul, Province of Tawi-Tawi, to Hadji Imam Banjal Elementary School
Section 1. The name of the Manuk Mangkaw East Elementary School in the Municipality of Simunul, Province of Tawi-Tawi, is hereby changed to Hadji Imam Banjal Elementary School.
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved: June 24, 1983
